N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 32.1 - Title and citation

State Regulations

Within and for the purposes of the Department of Labor
this Part may be known as Industrial Code Rule No. 32 relating to ski tows and
other passenger tramways and may be cited as Rule 32 as an alternative and
without prejudice to its designation and citation established by the Secretary
of State. Notes
